Parameters:
date - time of beginning of trace interval used to build spectra, we will find deconvolving responses for this date.
spectra - complex spectra
frequenciesArray - array of frequencies used to build spectra
resp - complex response
sampleRate - sample rate of trace
sampFreq - frequency interval (see Response#FreqParameters)
name - trace name
err - this string contains errors during building spectra and response.
